\par }
\par 1.  Select an objects to rename.
\par 2.  Right click over the icon.
\par 3.  Choose Rename from the popup menu.
\par 
\par {\b Creating a folder}{\b 
\par }
\par 1.  Open the parent folder as an icon window.
\par 2.  Right click in the space between the icons.
\par 3.  Select Create Folder from the menu.
