\par \pard\plain \f3\fs20\lang2057 {\f2 
This general keyboard-shortcut facility works from any window of Calmira, and lets you assign a Ctrl+Alt key combination to a window, menu item or desktop shortcut.  Fill the [Keyboard] section of the INI file with the desired mappings in the format capti
