\par }{\f2 
When you press Ctrl+Alt together with another key, Calmira searches this list and obtains the caption.  It then searches all windows, shortcuts, and the start menu for a match (in that order), and activates the object if a matching caption is found.  If y
}{\f2 ou specify a folder which is not shown in a window, then the folder is opened for you.}{\f2 
\par }{\f2 
