\par }{\f2 
\par }\pard\plain \s5 \f2\fs20\lang2057 In the above example, Ctrl+Alt+F1 will restore your system window.  Ctrl+Alt+C might activate a shortcut to drive C.  Ctrl+Alt+W will open the windows folder, and Ctrl+Alt+N could run Notepad if it's in the Start menu.  

